artworks.title: Nighthawks
artworks.alt_text: Scene in a diner, viewed through wrap-around glass windows, at night on an empty urban street. A light-skinned man and woman, he in a suit and she in a red dress, sit together at a triangular wood bar, eyes downcast. At left sits another man, his back to the viewer. Behind the counter is a light-skinned man in a white uniform. The interior lights cast a yellow glow that spills onto the street in pale green. Above the diner a sign reads, "Phillies".

artworks.title: Sky above Clouds IV
artworks.alt_text: A work made of oil on canvas.

artworks.title: American Gothic
artworks.alt_text: Painting of a woman and an older white man holding a pitchfork, both seen from the waist up. They stand side by side with stern expressions, in front of a white house with a peaked roof.

artworks.title: The Bedroom
artworks.alt_text: Painting of bedroom, blue walls, green window, tan bed, red bedding.

artworks.title: A Sunday on La Grande Jatte
artworks.alt_text: Large painting of people in a crowded park, brushstrokes are dots.

artworks.title: The Old Guitarist
artworks.alt_text: Painting, mostly in shades of blue, of a thin, bent, older man wearing ragged clothes and sitting cross-legged playing a guitar positioned upright in his lap.

artworks.title: Self-Portrait
artworks.alt_text: Painting of a red-haired, bearded man with light skin, painted in short brushstrokes and multicolored dots. The background is likewise a mass of small, closely spaced colored dots, these in green, blue, and red-orange.

artworks.title: Arrival of the Normandy Train, Gare Saint-Lazare
artworks.alt_text: Loosely painted image of an open-air train station. On the right, a parked train gives off an enormous plumb of white smoke, making the scene look as though it were full of clouds. A huddled mass of barely discernible people crowd around the train on both sides of the tracks. Blue, green, and gray tones dominate.

artworks.title: Inventions of the Monsters
artworks.alt_text: Painting of stark landscape populated by strange figures, everyday objects, and a burning giraffe.

artworks.title: The Bay of Marseille, Seen from L’Estaque
artworks.alt_text: Impressionist sea landscape, tan houses, blue ocean, distant mountains.

artworks.title: Lozenge Composition with Yellow, Black, Blue, Red, and Gray
artworks.alt_text: A square white tile, rotated 90 degrees, crossed by black lines intersecting at 90-degree angles. A few of the shapes thus formed—some partial squares, some rectangles—are colored in a single shade of yellow, blue, black, or red.

artworks.title: Woman before an Aquarium
artworks.alt_text: Painting of woman, arms crossed on brown desk, staring at goldfish.
